{
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": "-- Grafana --",
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "description": "CDN Image Performance — LCP, carousel load times, error rates, and variant completeness",
  "editable": true,
  "gnetId": null,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "title": "🖼️ Image LCP (P95) — Target: < 3s",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(http_image_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "LCP P95"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 10,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 2.5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 3 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "📉 Image Error Rate — Target: < 20%",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(http_image_request_errors_total{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m]) / rate(http_image_requests_total{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Error Rate %"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 10 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 20 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "🎠 Carousel Load Time (P95)",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(http_carousel_load_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Carousel P95"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 15,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 8 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "📸 Images Processing Queue",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rabbitmq_queue_messages{queue=\"process.media.queue\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Pending"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 50 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 100 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "Image LCP Over Time",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, rate(http_image_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "P50"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(http_image_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "P95"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, rate(http_image_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "P99"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 3 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "Image Error Rate Over Time",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(http_image_request_errors_total{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m]) / rate(http_image_requests_total{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "Error Rate %"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 20
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 20 }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "CDN Response Time Distribution",
      "type": "heatmap",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 18 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(http_image_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service=\"mediaservice\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "{{le}}",
          "format": "heatmap"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Image Variant Completeness",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 18 },
      "description": "Track images with complete vs incomplete variants (thumb, small, medium, large, webp)",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "media_images_total{status=\"processed\"}",
          "legendFormat": "Total Processed"
        },
        {
          "expr": "media_images_missing_variants_total",
          "legendFormat": "Missing Variants"
        },
        {
          "expr": "media_images_requeued_total",
          "legendFormat": "Re-queued for Processing"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "title": "Synthetic Monitor Results (GitHub Actions)",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 28 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## 📸 Synthetic CDN Monitor\n\nThe **Synthetic CDN Monitor** GitHub Actions workflow runs every 30 minutes and measures:\n\n- **Image LCP** from a simulated 4G connection in Santo Domingo (100ms latency, 20Mbps)\n- **Carousel load time** for the most visited listing\n- **Image error rate** (broken CDN URLs)\n\n### Thresholds\n| Metric | Good | Warning | Critical |\n|--------|------|---------|----------|\n| Image LCP | < 2.5s | 2.5-3s | > 3s |\n| Error Rate | < 10% | 10-20% | > 20% |\n| Carousel Load | < 5s | 5-8s | > 8s |\n\n📍 Results: [GitHub Actions → Synthetic CDN Monitor](../../actions/workflows/synthetic-cdn-monitor.yml)"
      }
    }
  ],
  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 37,
  "style": "dark",
  "tags": ["cdn", "performance", "images", "media"],
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "America/Santo_Domingo",
  "title": "CDN Image Performance",
  "uid": "cdn-image-performance",
  "version": 1
